config FUJITSU_PROXIMITY_DRIVER
	bool "Fujitsu Proximity sensor Devices driver"
	default y
	---help---
	  If you say yes here you get support for the Proximity sensor
	  chips.

	  This driver can also be built as a module. If so, the module
	  will be called proximity sensor.

config FUJITSU_ILLUMI_DRIVER
	bool "Fujitsu Illuminance sensor Devices driver"
	depends on FUJITSU_PROXIMITY_DRIVER
	default y
	---help---
	  If you say yes here you get support for the Illuminance
	  sensor chips.

	  This driver can also be built as a module. If so, the module
	  will be called proximity sensor.

